Installation procedure:

1. Download anaconda from the webpage and install.
2. Create a new Virtual Environment (using conda create) with python >3.6 
3. Switch to that virtual environment (using conda activate)
4. Install the following packages:
    a. Python 3.6
    b. Matplotlib
    c. Numpy
    d. Scipy
    e. Scikit-learn
    f. Tensorflow 2.0
    g. Pandas
    h. Theano
5. A text editor of your choice (Spyder is good for large data, vscode for extensibility, Jupyter is widely used everywhere)
